  explanation = 'The passage is organized to explain a cause-and-effect relationship supported by field evidence, moving from context to evidence to implication. Choice A names that rhetorical structure accurately. The distractors misread the passage as unstructured, anti-science, or biographical when it is explanatory and evidence-driven throughout.',
